; : 161 974 1650 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 974 M 
-0.200 0 (     2.4\) Change the grammar for elaborated-type-specifier to say:)A 
; : 161 1064 900 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1064 M 
-0.200 0 (          elaborated-type-specifier:)A 
; : 161 1109 1575 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
