161 1244 M 
-0.200 0 (     |     typename ::opt nested-name-specifier template opt template-id)A 
; : 161 1334 1825 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1334 M 
-0.200 0 (   In the discussions in the small group, Bill, Josee \(and I believe John)A 
; : 161 1379 1850 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
161 1379 M 
-0.200 0 (   as well\) preferred 2\). Anthony strongly disagreed with 2\) and preferred)A 
; : 161 1424 1800 45 rc 0 0 0 sco F0_42
Ji 
